reviewText: Great movie, much better than expected
I really enjoyed watching this movie and recommend you guys to check it out. You won't regret it.
A throw back to the film noir style movies mixed with suspense. Action. And drama.

Fast pace twisted roller coaster film with great artistic cinematography and realistic story. This movie clearly shows what an artistic and creative director and writer can make with a low budget. Story is has a very fast and intense pace, acting was surprisingly very good, editing of the movie was insane and very well executed!!!
2015NR: A prime example of what you get when people submit fake good-ratings on Amazon ... a total waste of time. No more need be said.
